Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.70,0:00:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.85,0:00:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翌晨的陽光就快來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.06,0:00:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照進這間充滿煙蒂\N雜亂無章的屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.83,0:00:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Tell me why 聖母瑪利亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.80,0:00:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對溫柔感到飢渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.14,0:00:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Tell me why
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.84,0:00:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼孤單的夜晚\N總是如此漫長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.72,0:00:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牛仔褲下的膝蓋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.62,0:00:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被破碎的夢想打溼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.96,0:01:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿著襯衫的胸部太過耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.96,0:01:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.44,0:01:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對喔,夏日廟會快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.19,0:02:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.90,0:02:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回來啦\N今天拜訪公司成績如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.37,0:02:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,還好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.14,0:02:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,這是我的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.21,0:02:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,由加里奶奶寄來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.11,0:02:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這實在太感謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.68,0:02:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感謝什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.95,0:02:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.38,0:02:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.82,0:02:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要亂拆啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.55,0:02:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.12,0:02:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.62,0:02:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是浴衣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.72,0:02:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了,趕上明天的夏日廟會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.29,0:02:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑\N我現在忙著找工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.76,0:02:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這信上寫著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.37,0:02:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色這件浴衣\N是為管理員特別做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.54,0:02:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是情人裝耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.87,0:02:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代\N這下你非去夏日廟會不可了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.44,0:03:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.70,0:03:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#71仲夏夜之夢?\N五代就要找到工作了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.98,0:03:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.21,0:03:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.28,0:03:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也要去拜訪公司嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.22,0:03:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,今天想去拜訪三家公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.55,0:03:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請好好加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.36,0:03:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.69,0:03:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.83,0:03:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.73,0:03:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你奶奶送我的浴衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.53,0:03:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不客氣,大小合身嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.13,0:03:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很合身,剛剛好\N我今晚就會來穿穿看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.74,0:04:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很期待,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.64,0:04:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,是三鷹寄來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.85,0:04:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炎炎夏日,妳過得好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.28,0:04:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.62,0:04:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我終於脫胎換骨重生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.92,0:04:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有重要的事\N想在最近見妳一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.96,0:04:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重要的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.56,0:04:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是關於上次那件\N不了了之的求婚嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.03,0:04:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,好可愛的小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.84,0:04:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是為什麼要用小狗的照片?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來啊,麥肯諾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.88,0:04:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好,好乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.02,0:04:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個大騙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.32,0:04:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是說你討厭小狗\N討厭得要死嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.75,0:04:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叔叔,你聽過忍者的修行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.66,0:04:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.23,0:04:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍者為了培養跳躍能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.30,0:05:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天跳過逐漸成長中的樹芽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.00,0:05:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後終於能跳過大樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.28,0:05:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.74,0:05:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狗也是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.35,0:05:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從小時候就開始養\N只要慢慢習慣牠…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.98,0:05:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這次的嘗試非常成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是一件好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.06,0:05:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼一來,跟愛狗的\N明日菜小姐的婚事就好談了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.76,0:05:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要提這種八百年前的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.67,0:05:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的目標只為了這隻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.13,0:05:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只為了輕撫這隻狗的頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.87,0:05:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我歷經了嘔心瀝血的特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.67,0:06:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請保佑我能順利找到工作\N能向響子求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.94,0:06:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她穿浴衣的模樣,好美喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.05,0:06:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,兩位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.98,0:06:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你在祈求些什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.12,0:06:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有什麼,我在祈求能找到工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.06,0:06:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當…當然!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.96,0:06:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個\N站在一起給我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.50,0:06:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.43,0:06:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此,你奶奶的判斷\N果然是正確的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.11,0:06:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要一直盯著人家看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.11,0:06:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係\N你們很像一對夫妻喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.55,0:06:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.75,0:06:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有現在而已喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.68,0:07:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賢太郎,我們去逛攤位吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.39,0:07:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我想玩射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.22,0:07:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽,我想吃魷魚\N買給我吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.60,0:07:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這應該也算是狗…吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.05,0:07:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.29,0:07:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.30,0:07:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽,再給我一百圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.21,0:07:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.67,0:07:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賢太郎,我的給你打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.11,0:08:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨,大家好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.55,0:08:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.58,0:08:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去妳那邊找妳\N可是都沒人在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.15,0:08:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我想可能在這裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.66,0:08:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.83,0:08:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼,五代也在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.50,0:08:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音無小姐\N妳看了我的問候信了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.80,0:08:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.83,0:08:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼問候信?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.17,0:08:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪,惣一郎呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.14,0:08:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭,惣一郎跑到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.81,0:08:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可不行,快點去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.08,0:08:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定得去找才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.18,0:08:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.55,0:08:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼,我往那邊找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.12,0:08:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,難道三鷹已經不怕狗了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.23,0:08:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.96,0:08:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是我們也快去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.00,0:09:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之,得先把惣一郎找到\N不然一切都沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.71,0:09:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果三鷹真的已經不怕狗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.38,0:09:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.02,0:09:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四…四谷,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.66,0:09:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天是課外教學的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.96,0:09:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看,我們兩個很登對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.87,0:09:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託,我現在沒空跟妳扯這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.15,0:09:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來來來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.35,0:10:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.32,0:10:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,這不是惣一郎嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.49,0:10:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.21,0:10:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,你跑到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.98,0:10:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害我好擔心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.65,0:10:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.86,0:11:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.29,0:11:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.60,0:11:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙…臉皮還真厚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.07,0:11:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到牠了,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.77,0:11:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.78,0:11:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.19,0:11:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音無小姐,這樣妳明白了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.36,0:11:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.10,0:11:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.89,0:12:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹一定吃了不少苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.33,0:12:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來這下敲定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.30,0:12:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.17,0:12:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹已經沒有弱點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.80,0:12:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是跟他比起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.67,0:12:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,情敵五代卻連工作都還找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.98,0:12:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹那次不了了之的求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.81,0:12:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許最近會再提出來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.48,0:12:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,這個可能性很高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.33,0:12:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,這下事情嚴重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.50,0:12:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千萬不能退縮唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.93,0:12:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,男人就得提起勇氣才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.64,0:12:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.94,0:12:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別人給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.21,0:12:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰給妳的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.51,0:13:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個叫三鷹的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.25,0:13:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.28,0:13:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.46,0:13:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乾杯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.73,0:13:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,真好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.20,0:13:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的棒透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.64,0:13:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老闆,再來兩杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.04,0:13:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.27,0:13:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.98,0:13:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.41,0:13:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還不用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.48,0:13:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了,無精打采的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.08,0:13:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在擔心找工作的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.35,0:13:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天不要提這件事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.86,0:13:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他好像想進一流企業工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.33,0:13:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一流企業啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.40,0:13:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,你一定有人脈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才沒有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.07,0:14:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你唸的大學\N沒有人脈也進得了一流企業嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.24,0:14:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不要瞧不起人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.18,0:14:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算我們學校,也可以憑實力\N進入四井產物和三友商事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概五年出一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.49,0:14:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三友商事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.35,0:14:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之,不要談這件事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.36,0:14:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代老師,你想進三友商事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.36,0:14:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,如果進得去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八神,怎麼啦?\N妳好像很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.40,0:14:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我爸爸是\N三友商事的人事部長啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.95,0:14:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這是真的,你怎麼辦?\N五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.82,0:14:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼,原來是開玩笑啊\N妳好壞喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.26,0:15:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心,五代就算沒有人脈\N也是五年出一個的傑出人才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.93,0:15:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳在挖苦我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.43,0:15:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,不要再談這個了\N聊一些別的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.34,0:15:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.47,0:15:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳這件浴衣是今年新做的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.21,0:15:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟去年穿的好像不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.48,0:15:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看得出來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.75,0:15:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說到這件浴衣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.35,0:15:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是五代的奶奶\N特別寄來送給她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.52,0:15:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說,跟五代穿的是一對的囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.29,0:15:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,大家看了都說\N我們像一對夫妻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.83,0:15:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該也有人說''只有現在而已''吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.84,0:15:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.47,0:15:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為不論誰看了\N都會有同樣的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.43,0:16:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的\N這孩子竟然在這裡睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.47,0:16:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多該回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.00,0:16:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.71,0:16:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪,八神呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.48,0:16:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對喔,從剛才就沒看到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.44,0:16:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能在廁所蹲著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是也太久了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.35,0:16:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,螢火蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.93,0:16:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.35,0:16:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.32,0:16:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳怎麼一個人在這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.98,0:17:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好像有點累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.92,0:17:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天才從社團的集訓回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.72,0:17:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把腰帶放鬆點比較舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.23,0:17:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.43,0:17:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這會給五代老師的就業\N帶來不利的影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.96,0:17:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳在說什麼,我聽不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.90,0:17:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爸爸是個很嚴謹的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.27,0:17:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是腰帶鬆鬆的回去\N不曉得他會亂想什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.18,0:17:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那這跟五代找工作有什麼關係?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.45,0:17:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說妳爸爸是三友商事的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.19,0:17:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這或許是個好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.53,0:17:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爸爸對於見過面的人\N絕對不會忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.00,0:17:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果趁這個機會\N給他留下好印象的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.50,0:17:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八神,妳聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.30,0:17:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不是不明白妳的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.21,0:17:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過,妳冷靜的想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.51,0:17:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算當過女兒高中的\N教育實習老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.04,0:18:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也不算是什麼人脈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.55,0:18:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才要實際跟我爸爸見面\N然後增進兩人的感情就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.92,0:18:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要管我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.39,0:18:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會請五代老師送我回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.64,0:18:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?這麼說\N她爸爸的事是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.61,0:18:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.92,0:18:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是夠了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.65,0:18:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我現在的處境很艱苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.65,0:18:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我也沒必要這麼巴結…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這我倒是沒意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.96,0:18:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟你教過的學生\N現在身體不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.76,0:18:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送她回去也是老師的職責吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.30,0:18:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.01,0:19:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最不擅長自我推薦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.18,0:19:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣做也很不道德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把她放在門口後就回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.99,0:19:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼八神,或許妳會覺得我很無情\N不過我就送到這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.80,0:19:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起喔,老師\N我真的走不動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.88,0:19:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師,你要振作一點喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.05,0:19:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爸爸是個非常嚴謹的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.61,0:19:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最討厭邋邋遢遢的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.42,0:19:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳在說什麼,我馬上就要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.49,0:19:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊吹,妳怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.49,0:19:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您好,因為令千金身體不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.63,0:20:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師,老師,這是我媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.50,0:20:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用這麼緊繃,她不是我爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.37,0:20:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是那位家教老師啊\N謝謝你特地送伊吹回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.61,0:20:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓他進去裡面坐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.08,0:20:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不了,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.64,0:20:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這麼說嘛,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.18,0:20:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.12,0:20:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啦,都已經來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.06,0:20:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊吹,妳回來啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.72,0:20:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.89,0:20:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.26,0:20:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他曾經在伊吹的學校\N擔任實習老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.20,0:20:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我叫五代裕作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.23,0:20:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿這樣來真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.33,0:20:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我身體不舒服\N所以他送我回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.71,0:20:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸,我跟你說\N五代老師想進三友商事上班…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.04,0:20:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.84,0:20:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.75,0:20:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,別說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.15,0:20:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳快點換衣服睡覺去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.95,0:20:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.19,0:20:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,快點上樓去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.66,0:21:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要參加三友的面試啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.26,0:21:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.23,0:21:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…請您不要誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.00,0:21:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我送令千金回來\N並沒有其它的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.67,0:21:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這話怎麼說?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.71,0:21:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比如說,想藉機認識您之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.38,0:21:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也知道不可能只因為這點小事\N就得到您的讚賞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.29,0:21:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫什麼名字?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.89,0:21:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.39,0:21:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代啊,我會記住你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.33,0:21:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然你看起來好像笨手笨腳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.36,0:21:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是比那些明明很年輕\N卻油腔滑調的傢伙好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.70,0:21:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面試的時候再見吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.37,0:21:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,那我告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.68,0:21:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.06,0:22:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.86,0:22:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們聚在這裡幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.47,0:22:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等你回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.60,0:22:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人事部長怎麼說?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.84,0:22:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,還好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.61,0:22:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你這個表情好像蠻順利的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.08,0:22:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少我想沒有給他留下壞印象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.78,0:22:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.52,0:22:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下子三友商事是敲定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.55,0:22:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這還很難說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.99,0:22:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這得好好慶祝一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.52,0:22:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贊成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.99,0:22:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重新好好喝一頓,喝個痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.16,0:22:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?又要喝嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.26,0:22:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然要喝囉,慶祝你找到工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.07,0:22:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把希望抱的這麼大不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.45,0:23:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊吹,妳不去躺著可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.82,0:23:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊,不要緊,我已經好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.49,0:23:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸,起來啦,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.16,0:23:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你覺得五代怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.20,0:23:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯?五代?那是誰啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.50,0:23:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,伊吹,妳回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.41,0:23:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說,你什麼都不記得嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.88,0:23:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒用的啦,妳爸爸今天\N從傍晚就一直醉到現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.78,0:23:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.72,0:23:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?五代沒去參加面試?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.03,0:23:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是白痴,錯過了大好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.53,0:23:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他究竟跑去哪裡玩了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.80,0:23:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.33,0:23:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「嬰兒誕生?\N五代哭笑不得的人生!」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.64,0:24:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嬰兒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.44,0:24:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請…請不要說這種\N會讓人心臟負荷不了的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.42,0:24:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩人坐在黎明的護欄上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.84,0:24:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至今一直在尋找遺落愛的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.62,0:24:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.82,0:24:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳…一陣風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.19,0:25:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目光交會…只有…再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.27,0:25:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.37,0:25:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…在雨中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.81,0:25:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忽然…胸口…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.21,0:25:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夢…濡濕而發光

